last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 9
last_episode_to_air.overview: WWE Hall of Famer JBL joins the season finale episode to continue the conversation on WrestleMania 1, and how the future of the WWE was determined in one historic night. WWE Hall of Famer Booker T, radio personality Peter Rosenberg, and host Jackie Redmond explore exclusive stories and never before seen footage on the heated rivalry between Stephanie McMahon and Brie Bella.

name: WWE Smack Talk
overview: Featuring WWE Legend Booker T, Hot 97 and ESPN host Peter Rosenberg and WWE host Jackie Redmond, each half-hour after show breaks down the biggest moments from each Sunday’s “Biography: WWE Legends” and “WWE Rivals” as well as reveals new information that didn’t make the cut. Along the way, Booker, Peter and Jackie will welcome WWE Legends, current Superstars and other celebrity guests to further discuss the night’s events.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Glenn Jacobs, aka Kane, joins this episode to discuss unheard stories about Undertaker. Also, an in-depth conversation about Bret Hart & Shawn Michaels' bitter rivalry.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Former WCW President Eric Bischoff joins this episode to discuss Goldberg, and the decision to end his winning streak. Also, an in-depth conversation about two of the greatest characters in WWE history, Undertaker & Kane. Alongside WWE Hall of Famer Booker T, and radio personality Peter Rosenberg, host Jackie Redmond explores never before told stories and never before seen footage on WWE SMACK TALK.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Nikki and Brie Bella discuss their journey to superstardom in WWE as well as reality TV; an in-depth conversation about the two biggest WWE Superstars in history, "Stone Cold" Steve Austin & Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Paul Heyman joins the discussion with WWE Hall of Famer Booker T, radio personality Peter Rosenberg and host Jackie Redmond as they talk all that is WWE Hall of Famer, Kurt Angle. Plus exclusive footage, and never before heard stories on the Kurt Angle vs. Brock Lesnar rivalry.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: WWE Legend Lex Luger joins this episode to discuss his personal transformation and how today he strives to live his best life. Also, Lex Luger gives exclusive stories on the rivalry that was WWE vs. WCW. WWE Hall of Famer Booker T, radio personality Peter Rosenberg and host Jackie Redmond explore exclusive footage.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Are you ready?...WWE Hall of Famer Shawn Michaels joins this episode to discuss DX, and how the group revolutionized an industry. Then, a conversation on how the rivalry between HHH and Mick Foley helped define both of their hall of fame careers. WWE Hall of Famer Booker T, radio personality Peter Rosenberg, and host Jackie Redmond explore untold stories and never before seen footage.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: You think you know him? WWE Hall of Famers Edge and Beth Phoenix are welcomed by WWE Hall of Famer Booker T, radio personality Peter Rosenberg, and host Jackie Redmond to explore exclusive stories and never before seen footage. Plus, Edge reveals what the rivalry between himself and John Cena meant to him.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Rey Mysterio and his son Dominik Mysterio join this episode with WWE Hall of Famer Booker T, radio personality Peter Rosenberg, and host Jackie Redmond to discuss the rise of one of the greatest masked superstars in wrestling history. Plus, Rey and Dominik share their own stories of Eddie Guerrero that helped shape the rivalry between Rey Mysterio and Eddie Guerrero.

WWE Hall of Famer Booker T, radio personality Peter Rosenberg, and host Jackie Redmond explore exclusive stories and never before seen footage on the heated rivalry between Stephanie McMahon and Brie Bella.
